</td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td><b>x</b></td><td>
<p>The pixel's x&nbsp;coordinate.</p>
</td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td><b>user</b></td><td>
<p>User-supplied data that is passed to the callback.</p>
</td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr></table>
